      *    *-----------------------------------------------------------*
       gfx-000.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Subroutine per la preparazione dei valori rela- *
      *              * tivi alla valuta base, determinati dalla segre- *
      *              * teria                                           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "VB"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           move      s-dec                to   c-dec                  .
           move      s-asx                to   c-sgl                  .
           move      s-sgn                to   c-tdc                  .
           move      s-num                to   c-cdc                  .
           move      s-adx (01 : 20)      to   c-des                  .
           move      s-adx (21 : 20)      to   c-din                  .
       gfx-010.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Personalizzazioni                               *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       gfx-020.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione contatore righe                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-rec-num-rig          .
       gfx-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Apertura file di appoggio [kk0]                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Richiesta di un pathname unico alla segre-  *
      *                  * teria                                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      "UP"                 to   s-ope                  .
           call      "swd/mod/prg/obj/msegrt"
                                         using s                      .
           move      s-pat                to   f-kk0-pat              .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Open file                                   *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           open      i-o    kk0                                       .
       gfx-100.
