      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-iva-ibl-doc          .
           move      zero                 to   w-iva-imp-doc          .
           move      zero                 to   w-iva-tot-doc          .
       det-cst-iva-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Ciclo di scansione su castelletto iva           *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-iva-cst-ctr          .
