      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-gen-nat-iva          .
           move      spaces               to   w-gen-rif-iva          .
           move      zero                 to   w-gen-ali-iva          .
       det-nat-iva-050.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Forzatura preliminare: se il codice Iva, per    *
      *              * qualsiasi ragione, e' a zero, e' necessario     *
      *              * forzare al codice Iva piu' recente (22)         *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-gen-cod-iva        =    zero
                     move  00022          to   w-gen-cod-iva          .
       det-nat-iva-075.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se aliquota di omaggio                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
       det-nat-iva-100.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Lettura [zci]                                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      w-gen-cod-iva        to   w-let-arc-zci-cod      .
           perform   let-arc-zci-000      thru let-arc-zci-999        .
       det-nat-iva-200.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Test su natura operazione                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           if        w-let-arc-zci-nop    not  = spaces
                     go to det-nat-iva-500.
       det-nat-iva-300.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Eventuali aliquote strane                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Test su aliquota                            *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-gen-cod-iva        to   w-edt-iva-cod          .
           if        w-edt-iva-cod-003    =    zero
                     go to det-nat-iva-400.
       det-nat-iva-400.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se Aliquota imponibile                          *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Aliquota in comodo di due cifre             *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-zci-ali    to   w-gen-ali-iva          .
      *
           if        w-let-arc-zci-dec    =    1
                     divide  10           into w-let-arc-zci-ali
                                        giving w-gen-ali-iva
           else if   w-let-arc-zci-dec    =    2
                     divide  100          into w-let-arc-zci-ali
                                        giving w-gen-ali-iva
           else      move    w-let-arc-zci-ali
                                          to   w-gen-ali-iva          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad emissione                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-nat-iva-600.
       det-nat-iva-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Se 'Natura' definita in tabella                 *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Valore letto                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      w-let-arc-zci-nop    to   w-gen-nat-iva          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Normalizzazione Aliquota                    *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           move      zero                 to   w-gen-ali-iva          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Riferimento normativo                       *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           if        w-gen-rif-iva        =    spaces
                     move  rf-zci-com-int to   w-gen-rif-iva          .
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
      *                  * Ad emissione                                *
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
           go to     det-nat-iva-600.
       det-nat-iva-600.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Emissione tag <AliquotaIVA>                     *
      *              *                                                 *
      *              * '2.1.1.7.5'                                     *
      *              * '2.2.1.12'                                      *
      *              * '2.2.2.1'                                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
